===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# [[reasonable|Reasonable]]; not [[absurd]], [[foolish]], [[emotional]], or [[fanciful]].
#: '''''rational''' conduct''
# Capable of [[reasoning]].
#: ''Man is a '''rational''' creature.''
# {{arithmetic}} (''no'' {{compar}} ''or'' {{superl}}) Of a number, capable of being expressed as the [[ratio]] of two [[integer]]s.
# {{arithmetic}} (''no'' {{compar}} ''or'' {{superl}}) Of an algebraic expression, capable of being expressed as the [[ratio]] of two [[polynomial]]s.

